name: KLM 777-206ER [PH-BQD] Takeoff From Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Happy Heavy Aircraft Friday/Friday Fail :P

Here is one of KLM's Boeing 777-200s departing Calgary International Airport bound for Amsterdam on a sunny Sunday afternoon. I apologize for all the lousy camera work in portions of the video, I was having a bad day for filming :/ I hope you enjoy, nonetheless!
